title: Tyrese, Deon Taylor and Naomi Harris
itunes:title: Tyrese, Deon Taylor and Naomi Harris
description:
Today on the show we had the cast of the movie "Black and Blue" stop by where they spoke about the making of the movie, police interaction in the community and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to an officer who attacked a young girl and Angela helped some listeners out during Ask Yee
